      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TERRA FIRMA (1) stalked the lead after a clean break from the tricky draw and went on to finish second (28.03) at this track in a Novice race over 488m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Likely to feature again. DODGY DANNY (3) turned in a moderate run last time when seventh at this track over 488m behind Billy Me Goat (28.46) in a Novice race. Some good form is emerging from her last run. A forward showing wouldn't surprise. DEAR ELIZA (2) flew the lids and led throughout to get off the mark with her maiden win, then finished a 6 length fifth last start at this track over 488m (28.14). Returns to the course where she won her maiden. Expected to do much better this time. AKERMANIS (4) was well supported last time but could only manage third (28.06), beaten 2 lengths. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten.",
